    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
わが<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">日</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">本</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">もと</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">島国</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">しまぐに</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>よ<lb />
　<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">朝日</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あさひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>かがよう<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">海</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<lb />
　　<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">連</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">つらな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>りそばだつ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">島々</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">しまじま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>なれば<lb />
　　　あらゆる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">国</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くに</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>より<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">舟</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ふね</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>こそ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">通</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かよ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>え<lb />
<lb />
されば<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">港</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">みなと</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">数</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かず</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">多</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おお</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>かれど<lb />
　この<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">横浜</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">よこはま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>にまさるあらめや<lb />
　　むかし<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">思</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おも</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>えば　とま<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">屋</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">や</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">煙</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">けむり</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><lb />
　　　ちらりほらりと<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">立</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">た</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>てりし<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">処</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ところ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">今</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">いま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>はもも<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">舟</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ふね</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>もも<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">千舟</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ちふね</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><lb />
　<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">泊</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">とま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>る<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">処</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ところ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ぞ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">見</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">み</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>よや<lb />
　　<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">果</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はて</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>なく<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">栄</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さか</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>えて<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">行</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ゆ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>くらんみ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">代</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">よ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<lb />
　　　<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">飾</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かざ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>る<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">宝</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たから</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>も<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">入</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">い</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>りくる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">港</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">みなと</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
